56 SECTION 2.
57 Said article is further amended by adding a new Code section to read as follows:
58 "40-1-201.
59 (a) No ride share network service shall be liable under any theory of liability, including,
60 but not limited to, vicarious or product liability, for any injury to persons or damage to
61 property from the operation of a personal passenger car by a ride share driver by reason of
62 owning, operating, or maintaining a digital network or internet network to connect
63 passengers to ride share drivers for the purpose of prearranged transportation for hire or for
64 donation, provided that:
65 (1) There has been no negligence or criminal misconduct by the ride share network
66 service;
